      <ar>
         <k>ubhato-vibhaṅga</k>
         <def cmt="thing">
            <deftext>
               <b>
                  <c c="#a00149">Ubhato-vibhaṅga</c>
               </b>
               <br/>A collective term, comprehending the Bhikkhu-vibhaṅga and the Bhikkhunī-vibhaṅga of the Vinaya Pītaka. Sometimes the word seems to be used as varia lectio for Ubhato-Vinaya. <c c="#3b6bd3">Vin.ii.287</c> 
               <br/>
               <br/>
