                  <c c="#a00149">Usīraddhaja</c>
               </b>
               <br/>A mountain range forming the northern boundary of Majjhimadesa. <c c="#3b6bd3">Vin.i.197</c> 
               <br/>
               <br/>Location: <iref href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/???">???</iref> (Precision: 3, Type: hill)<br/>
            </deftext>
         </def>
