            <deftext>
               <b>
                  <c c="#a00149">Jīvā</c>
               </b> Jīvanti<br/>Daughter of Ubbirī, whose tragic death spurred Ubbirī overcome her attachment. <c c="#3b6bd3">Thig.51</c> 
