                  <c c="#a00149">Ṭaṅkitamañca</c>
               </b> Taṅkitamañca<br/>A place near Gayā. It was the residence of the Yakkha Sūciloma and the Buddha once stayed there. <c c="#3b6bd3">Snp.p.47f.</c>  
               <c c="#3b6bd3">SN.i.206</c> 
