               <b>
                  <c c="#a00149">Taṇḍulapālidvārāya</c>
               </b> Taṇḍulapālidvāra Tandulapāladvāra<br/>One of the gates of Rājagaha. Near the gate was the residence of the brahmin Dhānañjāni. <c c="#3b6bd3">MN.ii.185</c> 
               <br/>
               <br/>Location: <iref href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/Rājagaha">Rājagaha</iref> (Precision: 3, Type: building)<br/>
            </deftext>
