         <k>mahājāli</k>
         <def cmt="person">
            <deftext>
               <b>
                  <c c="#a00149">Mahājāli</c>
               </b>
               <br/>A Pacceka Buddha mentioned in a list of names. <c c="#3b6bd3">MN.iii.70</c> 
