                  <c c="#a00149">Mahāsubhaddā</c>
               </b>
               <br/>Chief queen of Mahāsudassana. <c c="#3b6bd3">DN.ii.169ff.</c>  
               <c c="#3b6bd3">Aii.189</c>  
