            <deftext>
               <b>
                  <c c="#a00149">Mahisavatthu</c>
               </b>
               <br/>A place on the Saṅkheyya Mountain where Uttara is said to have stayed, in Dhavajālika vihāra. <c c="#3b6bd3">AN.iv.162</c> 
