               <br/>Location: <iref href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/on the Saṅkheyya Mountain in Dhavajālika vihāra.">on the Saṅkheyya Mountain in Dhavajālika vihāra.</iref> (Precision: 3, Type: monastery)<br/>
            </deftext>
