         <k>mahī</k>
         <def cmt="place">
            <deftext>
               <b>
                  <c c="#a00149">Mahī</c>
               </b>
               <br/>One of the five great rivers of India, all of which have a common origin <c c="#3b6bd3">Vin.ii.237</c>  
               <c c="#3b6bd3">AN.iv.101</c>  
               <c c="#3b6bd3">AN.v.22</c>  
