         <k>rohīnī</k>
         <def cmt="place">
            <deftext>
               <b>
                  <c c="#a00149">Rohīnī</c>
               </b> (2) <br/>A small river dividing the Sākyan and Koliyan countries. A dam was constructed across the river, and the people on the two sides used the water to cultivate their fields.<br/>
               <br/>Location: <iref href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/27.64916, 83.54141">27.64916, 83.54141</iref> (Precision: 3, Type: river)<br/>
            </deftext>
