         <k>vetaraṇi</k>
         <def cmt="place">
            <deftext>
               <b>
                  <c c="#a00149">Vetaraṇi</c>
               </b>
               <br/>A river in the Great Hell. <c c="#3b6bd3">SN.i.21</c>  
               <c c="#3b6bd3">Snp.674</c>  It may be the same as the great “Caustic River” referred to in the Devadatta Sutta. <c c="#3b6bd3">MN.iii.185</c>  Its waters are sharp and bitter, <c c="#3b6bd3">Snp.674</c>  and the river flows by the Asipattavana.<br/>
               <br/>Location: <iref href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/"/> (Precision: 5, Type: river)<br/>
            </deftext>
