               <b>
                  <c c="#a00149">Vedhaññā</c>
               </b> Vedañña<br/>A family of Sākiyans. It was to them that the Pāsādika Sutta was preached. <c c="#3b6bd3">DN.iii.17</c>  From the Sāmagāma Sutta <c c="#3b6bd3">MN.ii.244</c>  it would appear that these Sākiyans lived in Sāmagāma.<br/>
