         <k>veṇhu</k>
         <def cmt="person">
            <deftext>
               <b>
                  <c c="#a00149">Veṇhu</c>
               </b>
               <br/>A deva who was present, with his retinue, at the preaching of the Mahāsamaya Sutta. <c c="#3b6bd3">DN.ii.259</c>  Veṇhu is a Pāḷi form of Viṣṇu.<br/>
